data.description: Discover the enchanting skies adorned with stars at the incredible Fantastic Airpark property. Equipped with a hangar for your planes, RVs, and various toys, this residence is situated in Aguila within the Valley of the Eagle Flight Park. The kitchen boasts beautiful custom Knotty Alder cabinets, adding a touch of elegance. With three bedrooms and two baths, the property spans approximately 7 acres, featuring covered patios on either side to cater to all your outdoor activities. The bedrooms are thoughtfully soundproofed for peaceful nights free from snoring disturbances. The property is serviced by Aguila water, propane, and septic facilities. Building permits for the hangar are readily available. you won't be disappointed.
